prudential plc puk company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile prudential plc puk related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialslife  health insurance overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse puk on new york consolidated usd  jul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description prudential public limited company prudential incorporated on november   is an international financial services company the company offers a range of retail financial products and services and asset management services throughout these territories the company operates through insurance operations and asset management operations the retail financial products and services include life insurance pensions and annuities as well as collective investment schemes its insurance operations include asia the united states jackson national life insurance company jackson and the united kingdom its asset management operations include eastspring investments us brokerdealer and asset management mg and prudential capitalthe companys prudential corporation asia has insurance and asset management operations across  markets and serves the families of the regions potential economies the company has been operating in asia and built performing businesses with multichannel distribution the companys jackson provides retirement savings and income strategies aimed at the number of people approaching retirement in the united states jacksons variable annuities offer a retirement solution designed to provide a range of investment choices to help customers pursue their financial goalsthe companys mg investments is an international asset manager investing on behalf of individuals and institutions for individual investors the company offers funds across geographies asset classes and investment strategies aimed at growing their longterm savings or producing regular income for institutional investors the company offers investment strategies to meet the longterm needs for capital growth or income it offers a range of collective funds which aim to grow their longterm savings or produce a regular income prudential uk is a provider of savings and retirement income products in the united kingdom the company provides longterm savings solutions for the united kingdom customers meeting peoples needs and retirement underpinned by its expertise in areas such as longevity risk management and multiasset investment eastspring investments the companys asset manager provides investment solutions across a range of asset classes including equities fixed income multi asset infrastructure and alternatives » full overview of puk company address prudential plc governors house laurence pountney hilllondon     ecr hh p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation paul manduca  michael wells  mark fitzpatrick  john foley  nicolaos nicandrou  » more officers  directors prudential plc news insurer prudential enters nigeria via insurance buy zenith bank deal jul   briefprudential appoints thomas watjen as nonexecutive director​ jul   thai bank scb halts  billion insurance unit sale as talks fail sources jul   update thai bank scb halts  bln insurance unit sale as talks fail  sources jul   britains bad bank repays  bln stg to taxpayers in  jul   » more puk news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialslife  health insurance home – prudential plc skip to main content customer websites prudential uk prudential corporation asia jackson mg eastspring africa about us how our business worksour strategyour customersour leadershipour history businesses asiajacksonprudential ukmgeastspringafrica insights the global savings gapeastspring’s  midyear investment outlookmike wells  finding new ways to invest in infrastructuregetting to know chinafinance in relati