 £ billion of assets under management …to do what we do… retirement income we invest customers’ savings to help them ensure they meet their longterm retirement needs £ billion of assets under management longterm savings we generate valuable returns for our customers through a longterm approach to investment  years of providing financial security protection we provide our customers with financial protection against illhealth loss of income and other adverse events  million life customers …for our customers our benefits we provide our customers with financial security and the opportunity to build a better future for themselves and their families  million life customers our people we provide an environment with equal opportunities career potential and rewards enabling us to attract and retain highquality individuals to deliver for our customers  employees worldwide our communities we support the communities in which we operate through our products the jobs we create investing in business and infrastructure and community investment  employees volunteer through chairman’s challenge key facts please see our fact file for key facts and information about prudential plcs operations around the world prudential fact file  april  prudential fact file   chinese april  privacy and cookies accessibility fraud  misuse of prudential name disclaimer site map rss alerts  prudential  prudential plc incorporated and registered in england and wales registered office laurence pountney hill london ecr hh registered number  prudential plc is a holding company some of whose subsidiaries are authorised and regulated as applicable by the prudential regulation authority and the financial conduct authority the prudential regulation authority and the financial conduct authority replaced the financial services authority on  april  prudential plc is a company incorporated and with its principal place of business in england and its affiliated companies constitute one of the world’s leading financial