 article is about the british company for the american company see prudential financial for places named after the company see prudential disambiguation prudential plc always listening always understanding type public limited company traded as lse pru nyse puk sehk  ftse  component industry financial services founded   years ago  london headquarters london ec united kingdom area served worldwide products life insurance investment management consumer finance revenue £ billion  operating income £ billion  net income £ billion  owner kelvin kharisma martin website wwwprudentialcouk prudential plc is a british multinational life insurance and financial services company headquartered in london united kingdom it was founded in london in may  as the prudential mutual assurance investment and loan association to provide loans to professional and working people prudential has  million life customers it owns jackson national life insurance company which is one of the largest life insurance providers in the united states and mg investments a europefocused asset manager prudential has a primary listing on the london stock exchange and is a constituent of the ftse  index prudential has secondary listings on the hong kong stock exchange new york stock exchange and singapore exchange contents  history  early history  twentieth century  twentyfirst century  operations  prudential ridelondon  swansea bay tidal lagoon  senior management  see also  references  external links historyedit early historyedit the company was founded in hatton garden in london as the prudential mutual assurance investment and loan association providing loans to professional and working people on  may  in  the company began selling the relatively new concept of industrial branch insurance policies to the working class population for premiums as low as one penny through agents acting as door to door salesmen the army of premium collection agents was for many years identified with the prudential as the man from the pru it moved to its traditional home at holborn bars in  and converted to a limited company in  the building was designed by alfred waterhouse and is built of terracotta manufactured by gibbs and canning limited of tamworth c — two of the same driving forces behind the natural history museum in london twentieth centuryedit holborn bars—traditional home of prudential the company was first listed on the london stock exchange in  in  prudential acquired the american insurer jackson national life in  prudential acquired scottish amicable a business founded in  in glasgow as the west of scotland life insurance company for £bn in  prudential set up egg an internet bank within the uk the subsidiary reached  customers within nine months but had difficulty achieving profitability in june  an initial public offering of  was made to allow for further growth of the internet business but in february  prudential decided to repurchase the  share of egg egg was subsequently sold to citibank in january  in  mg a uk fund management company was acquired in june  the company was first listed on the new york stock exchange to help focus on the us market twentyfirst centuryedit in october  prudential launched a new subsidiary pruhealth a joint venture with discovery holdings of south africa selling private medical insurance to the uk market in april  prudential outsourced its back office functions to capita about  jobs were transferred  in stirling  in reading and  in mumbai this significant outsourcing deal worth an estimated £m over a year contract built on prudentials existing relationship with capita who took over its belfast operation in  along with approximately  employees in a smaller operational restructure on  march  prudential announced that it was in advanced talks to purchase the panasian life insurance company of aig american international assurance aia for approximately £ billion the deal later collapsed and aia ended up raising money in an ipo in december  prudential announced the purchase of ghana’s express life company express life was subsequently rebranded as prudential ghana in april  prudential launched two corporate responsibility initiatives to support education in ghana the prudential scholarship programme for more than  senior high school students in partnership with the ngo plan ghana and a scheme to support actuarial science graduates in september  prudential purchased kenyan life insurer shield assurance and rebranded it as prudential kenya further expanding the company’s presence in africa on  march  it was announced that the ceo tidjane thiam would leave prudential to become the next ceo of credit suisse on  may  it was announced that mike wells head of the companys us business would succeed tidjane thiam as ceo on a pay package worth up to £ million operationsedit prudentials administrative centre in reading united kingdom the company has four business units prudential uk europe  africa the business offers pensions annuities savings and investments bonds isas they are particularly well known for the sale of withprofit bonds and pensions corporate pension schemes bulk annuities and individual annuities the company left the general insurance household car market in  licensing churchill insurance now part of the direct line group to use the prudential name mg the business offers investment management services including retail fund management institutional fixed income pooled life pension funds property and private finance part of mg prudential property investment managers specialises in the management of prudentials property assets prudential corporation asia based in hong kong the business is the largest uk life assurer in asia it has had a presence in the continent since  when an overseas agency for life assurance was created in india although this was subsequently nationalised prudential relaunched in india in  as icici prudential a  joint venture with icici bank as citic prudential life a – joint venture they were the first uk company to reestablish life business in china in  there are also businesses in hong kong taiwan japan south korea singapore malaysia philippines thailand vietnam and indonesia on  november  prudential corporation asia announced its intention to change the name of its asset management business to eastspring investments jackson national life insurance company based in michigan united states the business was purchased in  it was named after andrew jackson the seventh president of the united states of america and started business in  prudential ridelondonedit prudential ridelondon is an annual twoday cycling festival held for the first time in  the  prudential ridelondonsurrey  saw over  finishers and set a new fundraising record for the event with more than £ million raised for charity the event was developed by the mayor of london and his agencies and is organised by the london  surrey cycling partnership the main events are a mile professional road race through surrey and london and an amateur race along the same route participants in the amateur race typically raise money for good causes the  finishers in the  event raised more than £ million for charity the inaugural sponsor of ridelondon prudential has extended its sponsorship of the event for a further three years up to and including the  event swansea bay tidal lagoonedit in october  prudential announced that it will invest up to £ million in the swansea bay tidal lagoon power station a worldleading infrastructure project prudential has committed to invest £ billion in uk infrastructure projects over five years prudential will be one of the main investors in the scheme designed to harness tidalenergy which could power  homes for  years if approved the project would take two years to build and would create  construction jobs senior managementedit key individuals are chairman of the board of directors paul manduca group chief executive mike wells chief financial officer nic nicandrou chief executive of mg anne richards chief executive chief executive of prudential corporation asia tony wilkey chairman and chief executive of the north american business unit barry stowe chief executive prudential uk  europe john foley group chief risk officer penny james group chief digital officer alnoor ramji see alsoedit companies portal invest financial corporation richard woolnough prudential assurance company singapore a singaporebased financial services company referencesedit  a b c full year results  pdf prudential public limited company retrieved  april    a b c d timeline – prudential plc retrieved  december    fact file  pdf prudential plc retrieved  april    prudential plc investor conference  prudential plc retrieved  december    research page including details of many buildings that used gibbs and canning terracotta accessed  march   prudential plc london stock exchange retrieved  april    prudential plc to buy jackson new york times  september  retrieved  april    pru of britain in deal to buy scottish life insurancer the new york times  march   egg cracks internet for pru bbc news   prudential to swallow the egg whole bbc news   pru sells egg to citigroup bbc news   pru pounces on investment rival bbc news   prudential goes to new york bbc news   insurance boon for health conscious bbc news   prudential jobs deal with capita bbc news   prudential outsources  jobs in belfast to capita group the independent  august   prudential gambles on asia with bn deal theguardiancom  march  retrieved  april    prudential abandons bid for aia bbc news  june  retrieved  march    prudential moves into insurance in ghana the financial times retrieved  december    prudential increases capital base business and financial times  april  retrieved  april    jones sarah  september  prudential buys kenyan insurer in second african purchase bloomberg business retrieved  september    milmo dan  march  prudentials tidjane thiam to take top role at credit suisse the guardian retrieved  mar