 prudential property investment managers specialises in the management of prudentials property assets prudential corporation asia based in hong kong the business is the largest uk life assurer in asia it has had a presence in the continent since  when an overseas agency for life assurance was created in india although this was subsequently nationalised prudential relaunched in india in  as icici prudential a  joint venture with icici bank as citic prudential life a – joint venture they were the first uk company to reestablish life business in china in  there are also businesses in hong kong taiwan japan south korea singapore malaysia philippines thailand vietnam and indonesia on  november  prudential corporation asia announced its intention to change the name of its asset management business to eastspring investments jackson national life insurance company based in michigan united states the business was purchased in  it was named after andrew jackson the seventh president of the united states of america and started business in  prudential ridelondonedit prudential ridelondon is an annual twoday cycling festival held for the first time in  the  prudential ridelondonsurrey  saw over  finishers and set a new fundraising record for the event with more than £ million raised for charity the event was developed by the mayor of london and his agencies and is organised by the london  surrey cycling partnership the main events are a mile professional road race through surrey and london and an amateur race along the same route participants in the amateur race typically raise money for good causes the  finishers in the  event raised more than £ million for charity the inaugural sponsor of ridelondon prudential has extended its sponsorship of the event for a further three years up to and including the  event swansea bay tidal lagoonedit in october  prudential announced that it will invest up to £ million in the swansea bay tidal lagoon power station a worldleading infrastructure project prudential has committed to invest £ billion in uk infrastructure projects over five years prudential will be one of the main investors in the scheme designed to harness tidalenergy which could power  homes for  years if approved the project would take two years to build and would create  construction jobs senior managementedit key individuals are chairman of the board of directors paul manduca group chief executive mike wells chief financial officer nic nicandrou chief executive of mg anne richards chief executive chief executive of prudential corporation asia tony wilkey chairman and chief executive of the north american business unit barry stowe chief executive prudential uk  europe john foley group chief risk officer penny james group chief digital officer alnoor ramji see alsoedit companies portal invest financial corporation richard woolnough prudential assurance company singapore a singaporebased financial services company referencesedit  a b c full year results  pdf prudential public limited company retrieved  april    a b c d timeline – prudential plc retrieved  december    fact file  pdf prudential plc retrieved  april    prudential plc investor conference  prudential plc retrieved  december    research page including details of many buildings that used gibbs and canning terracotta accessed  march   prudential plc london stock exchange retrieved  april    prudential plc to buy jackson new york times  september  retrieved  april    pru of britain in deal to buy scottish life insurancer the new york times  march   egg cracks internet for pru bbc news   prudential to swallow the egg whole bbc news   pru sells egg to citigroup bbc news   pru pounces on investment rival bbc news   prudential goes to new york bbc news   insurance boon for health conscious bbc news   prudential jobs deal with capita bbc news   prudential outsources  jobs in belfast to capita group the independent  august   prudential gambles on asia with bn deal theguardiancom  march  r